(NULL, 'green', 'aporcella@cairn.edu', 'Adam Porcella', '0', '2020-01-27 9:00:00', 'During this year’s World Reach Week, you will expand your understanding of God’s calling upon a diverse world-wide church to carry out His work around the globe. You will be challenged to confront your assumptions about culture, the church, and missions. You will wrestle with your own perceptions and beliefs regarding what it means to love your global neighbors, and you will be inspired by the way God works through His people.', 0, 5, 'Academic Event', 'Various', 'World Reach Week'),
