(NULL, 'red', 'music@cairn.edu', '', '0', '2020-04-18 13:30:00', "Join President Todd Williams, Dr. Benjamin Harding, dean of the School of Music, and Cairn University students for a community hymn sing. Worship together through the singing of traditional and contemporary hymns, and hear a performance from Cairn's Handbell Choir.", 1.5, 1, 'Community / Student Event', 'Chatlos Chapel Auditorium', 'Hymns Sing'),
